title: Nomination of Seth David Harris, of New Jersey, to be Deputy Secretary of Labor | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House




March 04, 2009

 



Nomination of Seth David Harris, of New Jersey, to be Deputy Secretary of Labor




THE WHITE HOUSE  Office of the Press Secretary  _________________________________________________________________  For Immediate Release                                                 March 3, 2009    NOMINATION SENT TO THE SENATE:   Seth David Harris, of New Jersey, to be Deputy Secretary of Labor, vice Howard Radzely, resigned.
